Class OnMoveMultimediaListener

java.lang.Object

      edu.ualberta.controller.OnMoveMultimediaListener

public class OnMoveMultimediaListener
extends CommandAbstract<CallbackIntefaces.OnMove,CallbackIntefaces.OnUndo>

ONMoveMultimediaListener is the command for handling moving Multimedias. Since this varies alot between implementation, the user must stOnCommandExecute to define call back method act()
